sequenceDiagram
    participant Device as T265
    participant Reader as Reader thread
    participant Callback as Callback
    participant Latest as Latest state
    participant Queue as Multi-queue
    participant App as Application

    Device->>Reader: pose / IMU / fisheye samples
    Reader->>Callback: lightweight dispatch
    Callback->>Latest: update current state
    Callback->>Queue: push sample
    App->>Latest: read newest state for control
    App->>Queue: pop ordered samples for logging

